### Sources

- [ ] `GET /api/sources` — backend: `src/pages/api/sources.ts`, UI: **brak użycia** (w `src` nie ma wywołań `/api/sources`, poza mockami)

### Flashcards

- [x] `GET /api/flashcards` — backend: `src/pages/api/flashcards.ts`, UI: `src/components/hooks/useFlashcards.ts`
- [x] `POST /api/flashcards` — backend: `src/pages/api/flashcards.ts`, UI: `src/components/hooks/useFlashcards.ts`
- [ ] `GET /api/flashcards/:id` — backend: `src/pages/api/flashcards/[id]/index.ts`, UI: **brak użycia**
- [x] `PATCH /api/flashcards/:id` — backend: `src/pages/api/flashcards/[id]/index.ts`, UI: `src/components/hooks/useFlashcards.ts`
- [x] `DELETE /api/flashcards/:id` — backend: `src/pages/api/flashcards/[id]/index.ts`, UI: `src/components/hooks/useFlashcards.ts`
- [x] `POST /api/flashcards/:id/restore` — backend: `src/pages/api/flashcards/[id]/restore/index.ts`, UI: `src/components/hooks/useFlashcards.ts` (przycisk „Restore” m.in. w `src/components/flashcards/FlashcardItem.tsx`)

### Card Tags

